name: The Offering - Finger
description:
The Offering - Finger, 2022, Digital collage and drawing
So much depends on the keyboards of our devices...the enter key - "should I post that response...? Should I not...?" -- the delete key-- like it never happened, it goes back to the void.  A thumbs up icon to represent likes... Lala offers you a finger through the screen.  What will you type with it?
